dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents school districts for Wisconsin in 2013. The dataset was published by the Wisconsin Department of Public Instruction using data from the United States Census Bureau.[This polygon shapefile is a representation of Wisconsin school district boundaries for K-12 and K-8 school districts. These data were derived from the U.S. Census Bureau's 2013 TIGER/line school district boundary datasets.]
